ZH: 我家的屋顶上有一个烟囱。
EN: There is a chimney on the roof of my house.

ZH: 现代房屋很少有烟囱。
EN: Modern houses rarely have chimneys.

ZH: 如果你看到黑烟从烟囱冒出来了，说明有什么问题。
EN: If you see black smoke coming out of the chimney, it means there is a problem.

ZH: 煤炉的烟囱需要经常清理。
EN: The chimney of a coal stove needs to be cleaned regularly.

ZH: 不小心把信拼字错误丢进了烟囱。
EN: I accidentally dropped the letter with a spelling mistake into the chimney.

ZH: 隔壁屋子的烟囱里冒出了异味。
EN: A strange smell is coming out of the chimney in the neighboring house.

ZH: 烟囱的高度影响了火炉的排烟效果。
EN: The height of the chimney affects the ventilation of the fireplace.

ZH: 那座老房子的烟囱已经倒塌了。
EN: The chimney of that old house has collapsed.

ZH: 烟囱上的红砖正在被重新砌筑。
EN: The red bricks on the chimney are being rebuilt.

ZH: 孩子们兴奋地看着圣诞老人从烟囱里钻出来。
EN: The children excitedly watched Santa Claus climb out of the chimney.

ZH: 这个烟囱装饰得很漂亮，像一座塔楼一样。
EN: This chimney is decorated beautifully, like a tower.

ZH: 由于风向改变，烟囱里的烟雾往屋子里飘。
EN: Due to a change in wind direction, the smoke from the chimney is blowing into the house.

ZH: 烟囱上的套筒需要更换，以免起火。
EN: The sleeve on the chimney needs to be replaced to avoid a fire.

ZH: 据说这座房子里有一个鬼魂出现在烟囱上。
EN: It is said that there is a ghost appearing on the chimney of this house.

ZH: 上面的烟囱旁边有一只巢穴，里面有鸽子居住。
EN: There is a nest next to the chimney on the roof, where pigeons live.

ZH: 烟囱被白雪覆盖，形成了一个美丽的冬季景色。
EN: The chimney is covered in white snow, creating a beautiful winter scene.

ZH: 烟囱里的烟尘会对环境产生不良影响。
EN: The smoke and dust from the chimney can have a negative impact on the environment.

ZH: 烟囱是工业厂房中必不可少的设施。
EN: Chimneys are essential facilities in industrial buildings.

ZH: 烟囱上有个风标，可以指示风的方向。
EN: There is a weather vane on the chimney that indicates the direction of the wind.

ZH: 烟囱上安装了防雨罩，防止雨水进入火炉。
EN: A rain cap is installed on the chimney to prevent rainwater from entering the fireplace.
